    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/cbdf81a6b07595c3acf3f5563afe4a5b.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/cbdf81a6b07595c3acf3f5563afe4a5b.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/cbdf81a6b07595c3acf3f5563afe4a5b.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>将含有魔法的魔法块装备魔法书上可以使用魔法.</strong></i><br><br><br>附加一个相同魔法的魔法块会增强魔法.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/8edb52b3707a84da7316407aaa17dde4.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/8edb52b3707a84da7316407aaa17dde4.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/8edb52b3707a84da7316407aaa17dde4.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>如果不喜欢魔力块的形状,可以在魔法祭坛上变换形状.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/354ed939ff50d32135761d5684453a06.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/354ed939ff50d32135761d5684453a06.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/354ed939ff50d32135761d5684453a06.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>用魔力块完成魔法阵的话,会发动魔法阵的效果.</strong></i><br><br><br>可以自己的需要交换魔法阵.<br><br><br>可以通过拖放技能槽中的图标来更改技能的顺序.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/d6c60339dd8fba63e05bfac32ee49f2f.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/d6c60339dd8fba63e05bfac32ee49f2f.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/d6c60339dd8fba63e05bfac32ee49f2f.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/b0c83de8a59d7f38851b418a73892e29.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/b0c83de8a59d7f38851b418a73892e29.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/b0c83de8a59d7f38851b418a73892e29.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/65b5ddbf57d05ddca429668295c83a1e.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/65b5ddbf57d05ddca429668295c83a1e.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/65b5ddbf57d05ddca429668295c83a1e.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>可以探索具有独特怪物和首领的地牢.</strong></i><br><br><br>可以点击小地图上的图标,瞬间移动到你经过的房间.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/814f6c3be66176d8c6cfc2dec1390d1b.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/814f6c3be66176d8c6cfc2dec1390d1b.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/814f6c3be66176d8c6cfc2dec1390d1b.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在地牢里,你可以和卖药水和魔法块的哥布林进行交易.<br><br><br>收集怪物首领们拥有的宝石进入魔王城,打倒魔王!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/a1a07f20040e8f2c251d88df23dfa286.poster.avif?t=1721297192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/a1a07f20040e8f2c251d88df23dfa286.webm?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387310/extras/a1a07f20040e8f2c251d88df23dfa286.mp4?t=1721297192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
